## lambda

```java
//lambda表达式使用实例
val sumLambda: (Int, Int) -> Int = {x,y -> x+y}
val voidLambda: (Int ,Int) -> Unit ={x,y -> x+y ; println(" this is unit return method")}

println("lambda:"+sumLambda(10,10));
voidLambda(1,2);
```

## 常量&变量
```java
//常量和变量
